    <title>zer0ptsCTF2022</title>
    <url>/2022/06/22/zer0ptsCTF2022/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>一种费马分解</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<div class="note warning"><p></p></div>

<h2 id="Anti-Fermat"><a href="#Anti-Fermat" class="headerlink" title="Anti-Fermat"></a>Anti-Fermat</h2><h2 id="task"><a href="#task" class="headerlink" title="task"></a>task</h2><pre><code class="lang-python">from Crypto.Util.number import isPrime, getStrongPrime
from gmpy import next_prime
from secret import flag

# Anti-Fermat Key Generation
p = getStrongPrime(1024)
q = next_prime(q0)
n = p * q
e = 65537

# Encryption
m = int.from_bytes(flag, &#39;big&#39;)
assert m &lt; n
c = pow(m, e, n)

print(&#39;n = &#123;&#125;&#39;.format(hex(n)))
print(&#39;c = &#123;&#125;&#39;.format(hex(c)))
</code></pre>
<h2 id="output"><a href="#output" class="headerlink" title="output"></a>output</h2><pre><code class="lang-python">n = 
c = 
</code></pre>
<h2 id="solve"><a href="#solve" class="headerlink" title="solve"></a>solve</h2><p>设</p>
<pre><code class="lang-python">p ^ ((1&lt;&lt;1024)-1) = q0
</code></pre>
<p>则</p>
<pre><code>p + q0 = (1&lt;&lt;1024)-1 = 2**1024 - 1
</code></pre><p>p是1024bit的素数，q是p的每一位相反数的下一个素数，有:</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
p+q_0=((1<<1024)-1)=2^{1024}-1</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">
q_0=2^{1024}-1-p</script><p>我们就可以用$q_0$找到$q$，因为$q$是$q_0$的下一个素数，所以$q&gt;q_0$，即</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
q=q_0 + k=2^{1024}-1-p+k</script><p>所以模数n</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
n=p*q=p*(2^{1024}-1-p+k)</script><p>设$2^{1024}-1=A$，原式等于$p*(A-p+k)$，因式分解为完全平方式</p>
<script type="math/tex; mode=display">
p*(A-p+k)=p*A-p^2+p*k=p*(A+k)-p^2</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">
n=(\frac{A+k}{2})^2-(\frac{A+k}{2}-p)^2</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">
=\frac{(A+k)^2}{4}-(\frac{(A+k)^2}{4}-2*\frac{A+k}{2}*p+p^2)</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">
=p*(A+k)-p^2=n</script><p>设$a=\frac{A+k}{2}$，$b=\frac{A+k}{2}-p$，利用费马分解</p>
<pre><code class="lang-python">from math import isqrt
import gmpy2
from Crypto.Util.number import *
n = 
c = 

a = (2**1024-1) // 2
&#39;&#39;&#39;
while True:
    b1 = a**2 - n
    b = isqrt(b1)
    if b*b == a*a - n:
        print(a+b, a-b)
    a += 1
&#39;&#39;&#39;
p = 
q = 
phi = (p-1)*(q-1)
e = 65537
d = gmpy2.invert(e, phi)
print(long_to_bytes(gmpy2.powmod(c,d,n)))
</code></pre>
<p>output</p>
<pre><code>b&#39;Good job! Here is the flag:
+-----------------------------------------------------------+
| zer0pts&#123;F3rm4t,y0ur_m3th0d_n0_l0ng3r_w0rks.y0u_4r3_f1r3d&#125; |
+-----------------------------------------------------------+&#39;
</code></pre>]]></content>
